Devias ter ido ontem à noite.

247
00:17:09,841 --> 00:17:12,373
Ido aonde?

248
00:17:12,374 --> 00:17:14,274
Tudo bem,
vão todos mais tarde.

249
00:17:20,649 --> 00:17:22,716
