00:20:03,579 --> 00:20:05,101
Grandes coisas.

301
00:20:13,564 --> 00:20:16,689
O homem do momento.
Reverenciado seja.

302
00:20:20,737 --> 00:20:23,029
Malditos patos!

303
00:20:24,908 --> 00:20:26,709
Olá, meu!

304
00:20:26,710 --> 00:20:28,910
O que...
Merda, desculpa, meu.

305
00:20:28,911 --> 00:20:30,212
Tudo bem.

306
00:20:30,213 --> 00:20:32,681
